| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-1988 — Recovery Inhibition (blackbasta)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 2f9bc04a-b6bd-53ef-be29-9cf7643f8cec"
